        "content": "<p>Hi!<br>\nI've been finally able to get my FFI stuff working on windows, but something that's bothering me is, is there a good way to copy files in a lakefile to the bin directory?<br>\nSomething like how in C# you can do</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">ItemGroup</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Content</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Include</span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"s2\">\"Content</span><span class=\"err\">\\</span><span class=\"s2\">**</span><span class=\"err\">\\</span><span class=\"s2\">*.*\"</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">            </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">CopyToOutputDirectory</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span><span class=\"n\">Always</span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"n\">CopyToOutputDirectory</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"n\">Content</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"bp\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"n\">ItemGroup</span><span class=\"bp\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
